    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I found a great script for compiling ImageMagick on OSX from scratch via ThoughtBot's Paperclip installation instructions.</p>

<p>Unfortunately it didnt work perfectly out of the box;</p>

<p><code>bash
Undefined symbols:
“_iconv_close”, referenced from:
_opvp_to_utf8 in gdevopvp.o ...
</code></p>

<p>So a few tweaks to the script to installlibiconvtoo, as well as the latest stable ImageMagick and voila!;</p>

